ck1-r1","completed":true,"absolute_start_time":"2026-05-24T10:04:10.466000Z","absolute_end_time":"2026-05-24T10:04:20.739000Z","segment_id":"e4fd17d4-0659-4ff5-b945-5f6eb802540d:speaker-1:2"},{"start":23.678,"end":35.874,"text":"Thanks, Maya. This is Leo Santos. I will answer you directly and together we will test whether Vexa hears two named speakers in Google Meet.","language":"en","created_at":"2026-05-24T10:06:24.609568","speaker":"Leo Santos-compose-ios-pack1-r1","completed":true,"absolute_start_time":"2026-05-24T10:04:17.764000Z","absolute_end_time":"2026-05-24T10:04:29.960000Z","segment_id":"e4fd17d4-0659-4ff5-b945-5f6eb802540d:speaker-2:0"},{"start":35.874,"end":48.811,"text":"Vexa hears two.","language":"en","created_at":"2026-05-24T10:06:44.623726","speaker":"Leo Santos-compose-ios-pack1-r1","completed":true,"absolute_start_time":"2026-05-24T10:04:29.960000Z","absolute_end_time":"2026-05-24T10:04:42.897000Z","segment_id":"e4fd17d4-0659-4ff5-b945-5f6eb802540d:speaker-2:1"},{"start":43.045,"end":56.665,"text":"First Checkpoint, a developer calls the API Gateway, asks for a bot to join and Vexa handles browser control audio capture and cleanup","language":"en","created_at":"2026-05-24T10:06:44.623851","speaker":"Maya Chen-compose-ios-pack1-r1","completed":true,"absolute_start_time":"2026-05-24T10:04:37.131000Z","absolute_end_time":"2026-05-24T10:04:50.751000Z","segment_id":"e4fd17d4-0659-4ff5-b945-5f6eb802540d:speaker-1:3"},{"start":60.858,"end":63.698,"text":"I hear you. The second checkpoint is speaker labels.","language":"en","created_at":"2026-05-24T10:07:04.639374","speaker":"Leo Santos-compose-ios-pack1-r1","completed":true,"absolute_start_time":"2026-05-24T10:04:54.944000Z","absolute_end_time":"2026-05-24T10:04:57.784000Z","segment_id":"e4fd17d4-0659-4ff5-b945-5f6eb802540d:speaker-2:2"},{"start":63.698,"end":71.919,"text":"The listener transcript should separate Maya Chen from Leo Santos instead of mixing us together.","language":"en","created_at":"2026-05-24T10:07:04.639227","speaker":"Leo Santos-compose-ios-pack1-r1","completed":true,"absolute_start_time":"2026-05-24T10:04:57.784000Z","absolute_end_time":"2026-05-24T10:05:06.005000Z","segment_id":"e4fd17d4-0659-4ff5-b945-5f6eb802540d:speaker-2:3"},{"start":79.809,"end":80.549,"text":"and checkpoints.","language":"es","created_at":"2026-05-24T10:07:24.652014","speaker":"Maya Chen-compose-ios-pack1-r1","completed":true,"absolute_start_time":"2026-05-24T10:05:13.895000Z","absolute_end_time":"2026-05-24T10:05:14.635000Z","segment_id":"e4fd17d4-0659-4ff5-b945-5f6eb802540d:speaker-1:4"},{"start":80.549,"end":91.687,"text":"Buenos días, Leo. Vexa convierte reuniones de Google Make y Microsoft Teams en inteligencia de reuniones en tiempo real.","language":"es","created_at":"2026-05-24T10:07:24.651974","speaker":"Maya Chen-compose-ios-pack1-r1","completed":true,"absolute_start_time":"2026-05-24T10:05:14.635000Z","absolute_end_time":"2026-05-24T10:05:25.773000Z","segment_id":"e4fd17d4-0659-4ff5-b945-5f6eb802540d:speaker-1:5"},{"start":81.654,"end":93.915,"text":"Да, то есть сходить в дуть и попить кофе.","language":"ru","created_at":"2026-05-24T10:07:24.651853","speaker":"Dmitriy Grankin","completed":true,"absolute_start_time":"2026-05-24T10:05:15.740000Z","absolute_end_time":"2026-05-24T10:05:28.001000Z","segment_id":"e4fd17d4-0659-4ff5-b945-5f6eb802540d:speaker-0:0"},{"start":96.619,"end":107.959,"text":"French Checkpoint. Bonjour Maya, les webhooks doivent annoncer le statut de la réunion, les erreurs et la transcription finale.","language":"fr","created_at":"2026-05-24T10:07:44.667017","speaker":"Leo Santos-compose-ios-pack1-r1","completed":true,"absolute_start_time":"2026-05-24T10:05:30.705000Z","absolute_end_time":"2026-05-24T10:05:42.045000Z","segment_id":"e4fd17d4-0659-4ff5-b945-5f6eb802540d:speaker-2:4"},{"start":113.003,"end":124.697,"text":"Nice. Back in English, a support team can use Vexa to capture customer calls, action items, objections, and promised follow-ups.","language":"en","created_at":"2026-05-24T10:07:54.681937","speaker":"Maya Chen-compose-ios-pack1-r1","completed":true,"absolute_start_time":"2026-05-24T10:05:47.089000Z","absolute_end_time":"2026-05-24T10:05:58.783000Z","segment_id":"e4fd17d4-0659-4ff5-b945-5f6eb802540d:speaker-1:6"},{"start":129.524,"end":137.968,"text":"Enter develop a workload and fetch transcripts, stop the bot, store recordings, and connect the output to an internal product.","language":"en","created_at":"2026-05-24T10:08:14.687279","speaker":"Leo Santos-compose-ios-pack1-r1","completed":true,"absolute_start_time":"2026-05-24T10:06:03.610000Z","absolute_end_time":"2026-05-24T10:06:12.054000Z","segment_id":"e4fd17d4-0659-4ff5-b945-5f6eb802540d:speaker-2:5"},{"start":149.249,"end":158.747,"text":"Português e Checkpoint. Olá, Léo. Infraestrutura Cellfosteira ajuda equipes a controlar logs, armazenamento e retincal de gravacores.","language":"pt","created_at":"2026-05-24T10:08:34.693979","speaker":"Maya Chen-compose-ios-pack1-r1","completed":true,"absolute_start_time":"2026-05-24T10:06:23.335000Z","absolute_end_time":"2026-05-24T10:06:32.833000Z","segment_id":"e4fd17d4-0659-4ff5-b945-5f6eb802540d:speaker-1:7"},{"start":161.109,"end":170.929,"text":"Good handoff, Maya. A self-hosted point matters because teams want reliable logs and predictable data boundaries.","language":"en","created_at":"2026-05-24T10:08:44.702496","speaker":"Leo Santos-compose-ios-pack1-r1","completed":true,"absolute_start_time":"2026-05-24T10:06:35.195000Z","absolute_end_time":"2026-05-24T10:06:45.015000Z","segment_id":"e4fd17d4-0659-4ff5-b945-5f6eb802540d:speaker-2:6"},{"start":176.754,"end":186.692,"text":"For scoring, I am responsible for meeting intelligence, the API gateway, self-hosted deployment, and the final takeaway.","language":"en","created_at":"2026-05-24T10:08:54.714477","speaker":"Maya Chen-compose-ios-pack1-r1","completed":true,"absolute_start_time":"2026-05-24T10:06:50.840000Z","absolute_end_time":"20